Backend https://medicine-store-project-using-mern-ntc6.onrender.com




Vercel Deployment Process:
Vercel CLI (Manual Command)
If you don't use GitHub or want to force a deploy from your computer:
Install Vercel CLI (if you haven't):
code
Bash
npm i -g vercel
Run the production deploy command:
code
Bash
vercel --prod
It will ask a few questions (accept default settings). It will upload your local code directly to Vercel.